2020-03-12
----------
    How to work with command line arduino-cli
    -----------------------------------------
        1. Install arduino-cli 
            https://itp.nyu.edu/physcomp/resources/using-the-arduino-command-line-interface/
        2. $ arduino-cli core install arduino:avr 
        3. Compile
            https://arduino.github.io/arduino-cli/commands/arduino-cli_compile/

            $ arduino-cli compile -b arduino:avr:mega air_pump
        4. Upload
            $ arduino-cli upload -b arduino:avr:mega air_pump -p /dev/ttyUSB0
